oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Antique Archaeology: Rock the Rust (2011)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Advertising; Logos (Symbols); Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (brown and yellow on white) announcing Rock the Rust. Poster is an advertisement for the store Antique Archaeology, which is located in LeClaire, Iowa. Poster features a metal photoplate of the Antique Archaeology logo.
